%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Pylon%20team%20is%20pictured%20in%20the%20Seoul%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ba005432af4d666ef7492b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarty%20Kausas%20said%20Pylon%20spent%20%2442%2C000%20to%20take%20the%20team%20to%20Seoul%2C%20South%20Korea.%3Cp%3EMarty%20Kausas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20going%20to%20be%20spending%20about%20%24150%2C000%20to%20%241700%2C000%20to%20go%20to%20Hawaii.%20There%20are%20going%20to%20be%20about%2050%20people%20who%20attend.%20We%20basically%20booked%20out%20all%20the%20spare%20rooms%20in%20a%20hotel%20that%20we%20could%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20going%20to%20O'ahu%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20seven-day%20trip.%20We're%20still%20going%20to%20be%20working%20normal%20hours%20on%20Pacific%20Time.%20The%20sales%20team%20is%20geared%20up%20to%20wake%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20grown%20so%20quickly%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20a%20good%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20people%20together%20and%20have%20them%20focused%20on%20the%20team%20and%20the%20company.%20Usually%2C%20you%20don't%20make%20the%20time%20while%20working%20extremely%20hard%20to%20be%20social%20with%20your%20coworkers.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20give%20everyone%20the%20chance%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20some%20activities%20planned%2C%20like%20team%20dinners.%20You%20can%20choose%20between%20parasailing%2C%20ATVs%2C%20and%20turtle%20snorkeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Korea%2C%20we%20made%20a%20poll%20on%20Slack.%20The%20three%20top%20choices%3A%20Seoul%2C%20Bali%2C%20and%20Rome.%20For%20Bali%2C%20someone%20started%20complaining%20about%20mosquitoes%2C%20so%20that%20vetoed%20it.%20People%20didn't%20have%20a%20strong%20preference%20between%20Italy%20and%20Korea%2C%20but%20Italy%20was%20going%20to%20be%20twice%20as%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Hawaii%2C%20we%20gut-checked%20with%20everyone%20and%20asked%20around.%20Hawaii%20seemed%20like%20an%20option%20everyone%20would%20be%20excited%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b71d30a6-057a-44b2-a1aa-8f3491fd7f94%5C%22%3EWhy%20expensive%20off-site%20trips%20are%20worth%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20startups%20should%20do%20more%20off-sites.%20If%20you're%20well-funded%2C%20then%20you%20can%20definitely%20afford%20it%20and%20the%20money's%20well%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20people%20who%20come%20in%20six%20days%20a%20week%20now.%20I%20think%20you%20should%20reward%20people%20really%20hard%20work%20with%20really%20great%20rewards%20that%20are%20not%20typical%20of%20a%20bigger%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20the%20word-of-mouth.%20Our%20whole%20team%20is%20going%20to%20go%20tell%20their%20friends%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20Korea%20for%20nine%20days%20with%20our%20team.%26quot%3B%20They're%20obviously%20going%20to%20be%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20crazy.%20That's%20so%20exciting.%26quot%3B%20They're%20going%20to%20look%20at%20Pylon%20and%20be%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20cool%20company%20to%20work%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20fun%20is%20translated%20to%20everyone%20we%20want%20to%20hire%20or%20sell%20to%2C%20or%20will%20see%20on%20LinkedIn%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Pylon%20team%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ba0090f9db348adc0adeb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPylon%20paid%20for%20flights%2C%20food%2C%20and%20an%20Airbnb%20for%20its%20staff.%3Cp%3EMarty%20Kausas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20paying%20an%20engineer%20minimum%20%24150%2C000%2C%20and%20recruiting%20them%20is%20extremely%20hard.%20The%20cost%20for%20this%20trip%20to%20create%20signal%20and%20branding%20for%20us%20to%20prospective%20candidates%20is%20definitely%20worth%20it.%20It%20spells%20out%20the%20startup%20energy%2C%20versus%20being%20in%20a%20big%20company%20and%20working%20in%20a%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20are%20more%20stingy%20than%20they%20should%20be.%20They%20might%20be%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20not%20buy%20certain%20office%20snacks%20because%20they're%20more%20expensive.%26quot%3B%20In%20reality%2C%20the%20real%20spend%20is%20on%20hiring%20great%20people%20and%20retaining%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20exactly%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20many%20dollars%20into%20this%20type%20of%20activity%20leads%20to%20this%20outcome.%26quot%3B%20But%20my%20vibe-based%20finance%20here%20is%20that%20it's%20definitely%20worth%20it%20to%20encourage%20people%20%E2%80%94%20both%20to%20stay%20at%20or%20join%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-ceo-hawaii-off-site-trips-worth-expense-recruiting-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757233801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9ffde57d362d375e78eed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-ceo-hawaii-off-site-trips-worth-expense-recruiting-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pylon%20CEO%20Marty%20Kausas%20said%20the%20off-sites%20help%20recruit%20talent%2C%20reward%20hard%20workers%2C%20and%20differentiate%20from%20a%20big%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-ceo-hawaii-off-site-trips-worth-expense-recruiting-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Once%20Mocked%20for%20Growing%20Carrots%2C%20Punjab%20Farmer%20Now%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Cr%20a%20Year%20From%20His%2080-Acre%20Farm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20September%202024.%3C%