%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20maybe%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBoHL2HfBK1t%2F%3Fimg_index%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20parents%20met%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%201978%2C%20back%20when%2C%20in%20communist%20Romania%2C%20the%20Eastern%20bloc%20was%20the%20only%20region%20allowed%20to%20travel%20to.%20As%20she%20tells%20the%20story%2C%20they%20became%20an%20item%20in%20Saint%20Petersburg%20(known%20as%20Leningrad%20then)%2C%20the%20start%20of%20a%20shared%20journey%20and%20eventually%20travel%20(more%20so%20in%20their%2050s%20and%2060s).%20I%20remember%20their%20memorable%20trips%20to%20Egypt%2C%20Dubai%20for%20my%20dad's%2060th%2C%20visiting%20British%20friends%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20some%20Asian%20adventures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286568bd6-44d5-4204-9be8-29ed87067bbf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20mom%20is%20making%20up%20for%20lost%20time%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContinuing%20on%20independently%2C%20nowadays%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-asked-who-looked-after-kids-while-she-traveled-alone-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emom%20is%20living%20a%20second%20youth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20catching%20up%20for%20lost%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20decades%20of%20restrictions%20and%20work%20as%20an%20English%20teacher%20and%20tutor%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20academia%2C%20including%20the%20military%2C%20she%20travels%20more%20than%20I%20do%20these%20days%20as%20a%20travel%20writer.%20She%20blossomed%20instead%20of%20being%20isolated%20after%20my%20dad's%20passing%20and%2040%20years%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20most%20admire%20her%20courage%20to%20go%20to%20far-flung%20places%20in%20her%20early%2070s%2C%20in%20group%20tours%20or%20with%20close%20friends.%20And%20to%20keep%20as%20active%20as%20she%20doe