0the%20world%20on%20the%20steamy%2C%20dazzling%20Sambadrome%20will%20forever%20remain%20our%20most%20epic%20memory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20also%20share%20a%20love%20for%20art%20museums%2C%20spicy%20Asian%20soups%20(I've%20proudly%20influenced%20her)%2C%20and%20active%20exploring.%20Not%20the%20typical%20Romanian%20mother%2C%20her%20do-it-yourself%20approach%20is%20inspiring.%20She's%20a%20fast%20learner%20with%20technology%20(early%20mornings%20while%20I'm%20still%20half%20asleep%2C%20she's%20on%20Duolingo%20taking%20Spanish%20lessons)%2C%20a%20pro%20at%20using%20chopsticks%2C%20and%20surprising%20us%20all%20with%20her%20next%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe's%20had%20wilder%20experiences%20on%20other%20trips%20to%20destinations%20as%20diverse%20as%20Argentina%2C%20Iceland%2C%20Japan%2C%20Uzbekistan%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Laos%2C%20and%20Cambodia.%20Finally%2C%20this%20year%2C%20she%20is%20going%20to%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20future%20travels%20together%2C%20fun%20adventures%20surely%20await.%20She%20usually%20says%20yes%20when%20I%20suggest%20or%20plan%20something%2C%20and%20so%20do%20I%20when%20she%20takes%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-daughter-travel-world-together-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757182502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b1ed3a194a2d49b8af767d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-daughter-travel-world-together-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20mom%20is%20in%20her%20early%2070s%20and%20in%20her%20best%20era.%20We've%20traveled%20together%20a%20lot%20and%20people%20tell%20me%20I%20have%20the%20coolest%20mom%20ever.%20I%20agree.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Monica%20Suma)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%2