3Cp%3EWhen%20I've%20fallen%20asleep%20on%20planes%20in%20the%20past%2C%20I've%20missed%20out%20on%20services%20from%20flight%20attendants%2C%20and%20I%20assumed%20that%20would%20be%20the%20case%20in%20Delta%20One%20as%20well%20(I%20intentionally%20stayed%20awake%20until%20warm%20cookies%20were%20served).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20flight%20attendants%20ensured%20I%20got%20to%20enjoy%20Delta%20One's%20amenities%20even%20if%20I%20snoozed.%20When%20I%20took%20off%20my%20eye%20mask%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20flight%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20a%20flight%20attendant%20had%20left%20a%20hot%20towel%20for%20me%20on%20my%20side%20table%20rather%20than%20just%20skipping%20me%20when%20the%20service%20was%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20little%20touch%2C%20but%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20the%20staff%20was%20considering%20my%20experience%20on%20the%20flight%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20find%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20sleep%20despite%20my%20luxurious%20seat.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%20sitting%20in%20a%20business%20class%20seat%20on%20a%20Delta%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b75cada17a8c5b4053e39e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20had%20difficulty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sleeps-on-redeye-flights-overnight-trains-tips-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esleeping%20on%20planes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20was%20hopeful%20that%20my%20lie-flat%20seat%20might%20make%20it%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20disappointment%2C%20I%20only%20slept%20for%20about%20two%20hours%20of%20my%20nine-hour%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20time%20I%20slept%20on%20the%20journey%20to%20Europe%20when%20I%20was%20sitting%20in%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seat%20was%20comfortable%2C%20but%20other%20passengers%20and%20flight%20attendants%20moving%20around%20and%20the%20bumps%20of%20occasional%20turbulence%20kept%20me%20awake.%20It%20was%20still%20lovely%20to%20stretch%20my%20legs%20out%20and%20relax%2C%20even%20if%20sleep%20eluded%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20lastly%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20flying%20Delta%20One%20doesn't%20exempt%20you%20from%20some%20of%20the%20difficult%20parts%20of%20flying.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TV%20screen%20on%20a%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b75de8cfc04e97619c6fce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20excited%20to%20fly%20Delta%20One%20that%20I%20had%20no%20nerves%20about%20flying%20for%20nine%20hours.%20But%20the%20journey%20from%20Brussels%20to%20New%20York%20was%20actually%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20travel%20experiences%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2010%3A45%20a.m.%20CET%20flight%20was%20first%20delayed%20about%2090%20minutes%20because%20the%20incoming%20flight%20was%20late.%20Once%20we%20boarded%2C%20we%20sat%20on%20the%20tarmac%20for%20four%20hours%20before%20taking%20off%20for%20the%20nine-hour%20flight%20because%20of%20a%20mechanical%20problem.%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20get%20on%20a%20connecting%20flight%20to%20New%20York%20until%2011%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20home%20until%20after%202%20a.m.%20I%20ended%20up%20traveling%20for%20a%20full%2024%20hours%20before%20I%20made%20it%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-premium-select-worth-it-business-class-alternative-long-flight-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20some%20of%20those%20stressors%20easier%2C%20as%20I%20was%20served%20additional%20snacks%20and%20beverages%20during%20the%20long%20wait%20on%20the%20tarmac%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20cramped%20in%20my%20seat%2C%20like%20some%20other%20passengers%20on%20the%20plane%20might%20have%20felt.%20It%20still%20wasn't%20fun%20to%20wait%20for%20so%20long%2C%20though%2C%20especially%20before%20a%20lengthy%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitting%20in%20business%20class%20didn't%20mean%20the%20experience%20on%20board%20was%20perfect%20either.%20For%20instance%2C%20mine%20and%20several%20other%20passengers'%20TV%20screens%20weren't%20working%20when%20we%20boarded%2C%20and%20the%20flight%20attendants%20weren't%20able%20to%20fix%20them%20with%20a%20hard%20reset%20until%20we%20had%20been%20on%20the%20plane%20for%20over%20six%20hours.%20It%20wasn't%20anyone's%20fault%2C%20but%20it%20did%20make%20the%20lengthy%20time%20on%20the%20flight%20less%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelta%20people%20have%20the%20autonomy%20to%20offer%20on-the-spot%20service%20recovery%20in%20the%20uncommon%20event%20of%20inoperative%20in-flight%20entertainment%20or%20Wi-Fi%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Delta%20told%20Business%20Insider%20when%20contacted%20for%20this%20story.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20customers%20can%20further%20contact%20Delta%20to%20have%20additional%20concerns%20heard%20and%20additional%20compensation%20may%20arrive%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20One%20offers%20a%20standout%20flight%20experience%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20I%20know%20now%20it%20won't%20make%20flying%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-one-international-flight-surprises-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757158141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b754baa17a8c5b4053e29f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-one-international-fligh