5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%20startup%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98Energy24by7%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20home%20that%20no%20longer%20fears%20outages%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Suresh%20has%20relied%20on%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20iCUBE%202000%20inverter%2C%20paired%20with%20two%20iSTORE%20160Ah%20batteries%20and%20two%20545W%20solar%20panels%20on%20his%20rooftop.%20The%20system%20takes%20care%20of%20his%20daily%20load%20%E2%80%94%20lights%2C%20fans%2C%20pumps%2C%20motors%2C%20shutters%2C%20and%20routers%20%E2%80%94%20while%20cutting%20his%20Kerala%20State%20Electricity%20Board%20(KSEB)%20bills%20by%2045%20to%2065%20units%20a%20month.%20It%20runs%20mainly%20on%20solar%20during%20the%20day%2C%20drawing%20from%20KSEB%20only%20when%20the%20battery%20runs%20low%20or%20sunlight%20is%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20impressed%20me%20most%20is%20that%20the%20inverter%20draws%20daytime%20electricity%20directly%20from%20solar.%20Once%20the%20battery%20is%20charged%2C%20iCUBE%20shuts%20off%20the%20KSEB%20supply.%20If%20the%20sunlight%20is%20good%2C%20you%20can%20run%20600%E2%80%93700%20watts%20straight%20from%20solar.%20If%20the%20consumption%20exceeds%20that%2C%20it%20switches%20to%20KSEB%20seamlessly.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20notice%20the%20transition%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Suresh%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20Aliparamba%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iCON%20device%20enables%20households%20to%20connect%20their%20old%20inverters%20to%20solar%20panels%2C%20fostering%20affordable%20transition%20to%20solar%20energy.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-1-1756908818-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495988%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20iCON%20device%20enables%20households%20to%20connect%20their%20old%20inverters%20to%20solar%20panels%2C%20fostering%20an%20affordable%20transition%20to%20solar%20energy.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20put%20the%20system%20to%20the%20test.%20A%20storm%20destroyed%2025%20electricity%20poles%20and%20blacked%20out%20his%20neighbourhood%20for%20five%20days.%20Yet%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20office%20remained%20powered.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20that%20entire%20week%2C%20I%20was%20practically%20off-grid.%20My%20work%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20even%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20street%20was%20dark.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20student%20idea%20that%20became%20a%20solar%20revolution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%E2%80%99s%20story%20reflects%20exactly%20what%20Harsh%20Mohan%20(34)%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Energy24by7%2C%20and%20his%20peers%20dreamt%20of%20back%20in%202011.%20Then%20undergraduates%20at%20Amrita%20Vishwa%20Vidyapeetham%2C%20Amritapuri%2C%20they%20were%20searching%20for%20a%20meaningful%20project%20when%20they%20stumbled%20upon%20something%20simple%20but%20striking%3A%20nearly%20every%20household%20in%20India%20had%20an%20inverter%2C%20but%20these%20machines%20consumed%20power%20daily%20just%20to%20stay%20alive%2C%20often%20adding%201.5%20to%20two%20units%20to%20the%20bill%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20solar%20was%20making%20headlines%2C%20but%20at%20a%20steep%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CInstalling%20rooftop%20solar%20meant%20discarding%20your%20existing%20inverter%20and%20buying%20a%20new%2C%20solar-compatible%20one.%20It%20was%20unaffordable%20for%20most%20families%20and%20created%20huge%20amounts%20of%20e-waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20challenge%20sparked%20an%20idea.%20Guided%20by%20his%20professor%20Dr%20Vinod%20Gopal%2C%20Harsh%20began%20tinkering%20with%20a%20solution%3A%20What%20if%2C%20instead%20of%20replacing%20inverters%2C%20they%20could%20create%20a%20small%20device%20that%20connected%20any%20inverter%20to%20solar%20panels%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20this%20idea%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Energy24by7%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20way%2C%20households%20could%20adopt%20solar%20without%20buying%20a%20new%20system%2C%20reducing%20both%20costs%20and%20pollution.%20Our%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20solar%20accessible%20to%20middle-class%20families%2C%20not%20just%20the%20wealthy.%20Back%20then%2C%20panels%20were%20very%20expensive%2C%20and%20people%20thought%20solar%20was%20only%20for%20the%20rich.%20We%20wanted%20to%20change%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20device%20became%20%E2%80%98iCON%E2%80%99%20(Intelligent%20Converter).%20%E2%80%9CSuddenly%2C%20families%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20spend%20lakhs%20on%20a%20new%20solar%20system.%20With%20a%20modest%20investment%20in%20iCON%20and%20panels%2C%20they%20could%20turn%20their%20old%20inverters%20into%20solar%20inverters%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756