own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20%E2%80%98iCUBE%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20high-efficiency%20smart%20solar%20UPS%20that%20brought%20together%20the%20roles%20of%20iCON%20and%20a%20regular%20inverter%20in%20one%20device.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20inverters%20in%20India%20run%20at%20a%20lower%20efficiency%2C%20but%20iCUBE%20tested%20at%20an%20impressive%20peak%20efficiency%20of%2097%20percent%E2%80%94making%20it%20even%20better%20than%20the%20benchmark%20five-star%20standards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20efficiency%2C%20iCUBE%20was%20designed%20to%20adapt%20to%20household%20usage%20patterns%2C%20deciding%20when%20to%20use%20solar%2C%20when%20to%20draw%20from%20batteries%2C%20and%20when%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20grid.%20Their%20patented%20Battery%20Charging%20Inhibition%20(BCI)%20prevents%20wasteful%20charging%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20cutting%20hidden%20costs%20that%20many%20households%20never%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20says%20the%20appeal%20is%20immediate%20for%20middle-income%20families.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20lowers%20bills%20by%20around%2040%E2%80%9350%20percent%20without%20massive%20upfront%20costs.%20The%20setup%20keeps%20homes%20running%20during%20outages%20for%20days.%20You%20can%20monitor%20its%20performance%20through%20our%20mobile%20app.%20It%20is%20compatible%20with%20lithium-ion%20and%20even%20EV%20batteries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Energy24by7%20has%20more%20than%201%2C000%20customers%20across%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Karnataka.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-2-1756908862.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F